---
title: Seared Pork & Creamy Peppercorn Sauce with Mashed Potato & Steamed Veggies
description: This meal should be right at home at your place tonight. A nice piece of pork, smothered in a creamy peppercorn sauce and served with mashed potato and steamed veggies. Sometimes it’s hard to beat classic and simple.
